markings on it. He looks like a whole lot of trouble.
4488.room_name: A man in a mask stands here fingering the hilt of his sword.

4489.name: a masked woman~
description:
Very little of her can be noticed, aside from her femininity.  The
black of her clothes makes her difficult to distinguish from the
shadows, and a black mask covers her head.  She is short and somewhat
scrawny with a slender build.
4489.room_name: A woman in a mask stands here, looking edgy.

4490.name: Olivia~
description:
No more than five feet tall, this young woman has a large presence
for her small size.  Her skin is tinted with exotic lineage,
cheekbones high and chiseled, cheeks painted with the lightest touch
of rouge.  Falling in crinkled waves, her rich brown hair is kept back
from her face with a pair of braids, each accented with a weave of
golden ribbons.  She wears a tight fitting dress, gold in color, and a
pair of unassuming leather sandals.
4490.d_flags: D Coughs and sputters, groaning, '{5You will all pay for this...!{x'~
subroutines:
M hpcnt 4468 5~
M fight 4469 20~
M act 4467 vanishes into a vortexial rift!~
M death 4479 100~
4490.room_name: A petite brunette stands here, magic crackling around her.

4491.name: Markus~
description:
There isn't much that calls attention to this average man.  He
stands average height, with black hair cropped short and no sign of
facial hair.  Crisp and clean, his green tunic matches his eyes,
sleeveless and fitting snug to his scrawny chest.  The leather
breeches he wears are equally well kept, though they are loose,
covering the tops of his well worn boots. Large bags hang
under his eyes.
4491.room_name: A scrawny man stands here looking grouchy.

4492.name: Aryen~
description:
Bulging muscles are in full view on this heavy-set man.  He wears a
white wife-beater and a loose pair of breaches, slightly stained from
day to day use.  Behind his back, long brown hair is tied with a thin
leather strap, and in front he has a well trimmed beard. There are
dark circles under his eyes, speaking of exhaustion.
4492.d_flags: D Makes a final lunge, grunting with effort.~
4492.room_name: A large, wicked looking man stands here, guarding his mistress.

4493.name: a golem~
description:
Gray as the room he stands in, this creation of magic is huge.  It
stands perhaps 10 feet tall, its limbs thick as tree branches.  The
features on its face are chiseled into the stone, the only exception
being the clear crystals that have been set in for eyes.
4493.room_name: A massive stone golem stands atop the pedastal.

4470.name: a gate keeper~
subroutines:
M speech 4465 none~
M speech 4464 heroine~
M speech 4463 beetle~
M speech 4462 johnny~
M speech 4461 nine~
M speech 4460 dozens~
M speech 4459 meat~
M speech 4458 past~
M act 4476 drops a strange playing card.~
M exall 4484 0~
4470.room_name: An invisible force is here, enforcing the will of the mazemaker.

4201.name: the museum guard~
description:
The guard is human, and looks about middle age. His job, apparently, must be
well paid, for it is one hellishly boring one.
4201.room_name: A museum guard is standing at his post. He salutes you as you walk by.

4202.name: the poltergeist~
description: The spirit is pinkish, 6' tall, wearing white rags, and hold chains.
4202.room_name: A wavy spirit is floating here. It's a Poltergeist!

4203.name: the animal skeleton~
description: It is shaped like a large dog, with sharp teeth and everything.
4203.room_name: A skeleton in the form of an animal is here.

4204.name: the skeleton~
description:
The skeleton looks like that of an orc. He has a few ribs missing, and his
lower jaw is gone.
4204.room_name: A tall skeleton is shackled to the wall.

4205.name: the ghoul~
description:
The ghoul has recently been killed, or well preserved, for there is still some
blood pouring out of it's skin. It is wearing shabby rags, and its tongue hangs
down to its chin!
4205.room_name: A ghoul is here, contemplating your existance.

4206.name: the lacedon~
description: The lacedon is a form of marine ghoul, found on docks, and ghost ships.
4206.room_name: A lacedon is here, looking for his ghoul buddies.

4207.name: the ghast~
description:
The ghast is nastier version of a ghoul, with bigger teeth, large claws,
and a longer tongue!
4207.room_name: The ghast is here, looking for flesh.

4208.name: the heucuva~
description:
The heucuva appears to be a humanoid skeleton of normal size. His bones are 
covered by a robe that is little more than tattered rags.
4208.room_name: A heucuva stands here, waiting for you to kill it.

4209.name: the zombie~
description:
The zombie is slung against the wall. It is missing it's left arm, and quite
a few bones too.
4209.room_name: A zombie is slouched against the wall.

4210.name: the shadow~
description: It is dark, wavy, and disappears in shadows. It is shaped like a hideous demon.
4210.room_name: A dark shadow is stuck to the north wall.

4211.name: the JuJu zombie~
description: It looks a lot like a zombie, except it is more alive.
4211.room_name: A stronger than normal zombie is propped up against the wall.

4212.name: the wight~
description:
The wight is a nightmarish reflection of a human, with cruel, burning eyes
set in mummified flesh over a twisted skeleton with hands that end in sharp
claws.
4212.room_name: A wight is shackled to the wall.

4213.name: the giant skeleton~
description:
The skeleton is that of a huge human, with a firey magical glow in it's rib
cage.
4213.room_name: A giant skeleton is pinned down to the floor.

4214.name: the haunt~
description: The haunt looks like that of a retard, who has unfulfilled some life quest.
4214.room_name: A wavy form flutters though the air.. It's a haunt!

4215.name: the wraith~
description: The horrible creature is a black cloud, vaguely in the shape of a man.
4215.room_name: A wavy black cloud floats here... It's a wraith!

4216.name: the mummy~
description:
This mummy is clothed in rotting strips of linen. He stand 6 feet tall and
is obviously immensely strong.
4216.room_name: A drunken mummy is here, walking around the cage

4217.name: the zombie lord~
description:
The zombie lord is a living creature that has taken on the foul powers and
abilities of the undead. Zombie lords look as they did in life, save that
their skin has turned to the pale grey of death, and their flesh is rotting,
and decaying. The odor of vile corruption and rotting meat hangs about them,
and carrion feeding insects buzz about them to dine on the bits of flesh and
ichor that drop from their bodies.
4217.room_name: A still living zombie is sitting here.

4218.name: the banshee~
description:
The banshee appears as a floating, luminous phantasm of its former self. The
banshee is that of an old and withered elf, it's face a mask of pain.
4218.room_name: A groaning spirit (or banshee) is floating here, wailing.

4219.name: the undead beholder~
description:
This death tyrant is a rotting, mold-encrusted beholder. It is shrivled and
there are wounds exposing it's internal, spherical network of ribs, among
the remnants of its exoskeletal plates.
4219.room_name: A shirvled beholder floats here, being undead.

4220.name: the spectre~
description: It appears as a semitransparent being, in the shape of a human.
4220.room_name: A spectre is floating through the air, looking for life.

4221.name: the revenant~
description:
The revenant appears as a spectral, decayed version of its appearance at the
time of its death. Its pallid skin is drawn tightly over its bones.  The flesh
is cold and clammy.  The sunken eyes are dull and heavy-lidded but, when the
revenant faces you, the eyes blaze with unnatural intensity.  The revenant
bears an aura of sadness, anger, and determination.
4221.room_name: A revenant is standing here, looking for it's murderer.

4222.name: the vampire~
description:
The vampire looks absolutely human, cept for its pailing skin, and the dark
reddish cloak about, and its huge fangs protruding from its mouth.
4222.room_name: A vampire is standing here, as if it was frozen in time.

4223.name: the death knight~
description:
The death knight resembles a hulking knight, typically taller than 6 feet and
weighing about than 300 pounds. Its face is a blackened skull covered with shards
or shrivled, rotting flesh. It has two tiny, glowing orange-red pinpoints for eyes.
Its armour is scorched black as if it had been in a fire.  The demeanor of a
death knight is so terrifying that even kender have been known to become
frightened.
4223.room_name: A death knight clad in the armor of a solamnic night is here.

4224.name: the skeleton warrior~
description:
The skeletal warrior appears as a cracked and yellowing skeleton covered with
shards of decaying flesh.  Its eyes are black holes containing pinpoints of
reddish light. It is clad in the blackened armor and rotted trappings that
it wore when it was alive.
4224.room_name: A large skeletal warrior is standing here, hoping to free his soul soon.

4225.name: the {7ghost{0~
description:
The ghost looks like that of a half-elf, caught halfway between the prime material,
and astral planes.
4225.room_name: A ghost is is waving in the air, before your face.

4226.name: the lich~
description:
The lich resembles a mummy, being gaunt and skeletal in form. The creature's
eye sockets are black and empty save for the fierce pinpoints of light which
serve the lich as eyes.
4226.room_name: A lich is lurking here, looking very dangerous.

4227.name: the dracolich~
description:
The dracolich is a giant dragon that has been turned into a skeleton, but has
remained in its dragon form. Its eyes appear as glowing points of light floating
in the shadowy eye sockets.
4227.room_name: A skeleton dragon is standing before you.

4228.name: a squirrel~
description:
Small, furry, bushy tail - it's a squirrel!  What's a little guy
like this doing in a museum of creatures?
4228.room_name: A squirrel peers up at its visitors curiously.

4229.name: a dire weasel~
description:
Ferral and small, it is a weasel gone wild.  Its fur is dark and
its eyes cunning.
4229.room_name: A dire weasel flits around the shadows.

4230.name: a blink dog~
description:
Similar to a wild dog, this creature is slightly larger than most. 
Its fur is mangy and yellow-brown.
4230.room_name: Curled up on the floor is a blink dog.

4231.name: a dire badger~
description:
One might think this a typical badger if not for the subtle
increase in size and the keen glint in its eyes.
4231.room_name: A dire badger hides in the shadows.

4232.name: an orc~
description:
A mane of coarse dark hair frames his gray face.  Glinting red, his
eyes follow anyone who enters, and his lupine ears are slooped in
resignation to his fate.
4232.room_name: An orc crouches here, chained to the wall.

4233.name: an ogre~
description:
It's an ogre - big and ugly with an underbite and a low brow.  Its
thick hide is dull brown and its hair knotted.
4233.room_name: With thick chains around its wrists, an ogre is held here.

4234.name: a worg~
description:
It appears as a dark wolf, fur black and eyes shining yellow and
intelligent.
4234.room_name: A worg stalks around the room, growling.

4235.name: a dire ape~
description:
Furry and keen-eyed, this creature is not unlike an ape, though
larger.  Its fur is a rich, dark brown.
4235.room_name: Watching stoically is a dire ape.

4236.name: a unicorn~
description:
This create is beauty.  A white horse, its mane shimmers along
opalescent.  A tall, tapered horn rises from its head, glowly softly.
4236.room_name: A beautiful unicorn stands here, its room a cage.

4237.name: a minotaur~
description:
Thickly built and covered in brown fur, this beast is huge.  Long
horns rise from its bull-like head, and chains wrap around its arms
and bind it to the wall.
4237.room_name: Monstrous but tame, a minotaur crouches near the wall.

4238.name: a dire wolverine~
description:
Much like a wolverine, this beast has more intelligence glimmering
in its eyes than a typical wolverine might.
4238.room_name: A dire wolverine paces around the room.

4239.name: an owlbear~
description:
A sharp beak, dull ivory in color, is the main feature of its face
Small in size yet, this must be an adolescent, its coat of dark brown
feathers and fur not quite as thick as it will one day be.
4239.room_name: A small owlbear lays in the middle of the room.

4240.name: a displacer beast~
description:
The feline body of this sleek beast is covered in blue-black fur
and has six long legs.  Two muscular tentacles grow from its
shoulders.
4240.room_name: The shadows shift, a displacer beast roaming in their midst.

4241.name: a dire boar~
description:
A large boar, it smells of mud and dirt.  Its stout nose twitches
as it sniffs the air, and small tusks grow from its face.
4241.room_name: A large dire boar stands in the center of the room.

4242.name: a shadow mastiff~
description:
A great, black hound, its legs are muscular and its teeth sharp. 
Smooth and sleek, its coast barely catches the light, glimmering
darkly.
4242.room_name: The dark form of a shadow mastiff flits in the shadows.

4243.name: a girallon~
description:
Its four arms set it apart from any gorilla cousins.  Large and
broad-chested, this beast has thick, white fur and long claws.
4243.room_name: A huge girallon is chained to the wall.

4244.name: a dire lion~
description:
Its size is the only thing that separates this creature from a
normal lion.  Its mane is golden and its eyes keenly intelligent.
4244.room_name: Stalking around the room is a dire lion.

4245.name: a troll~
description:
The room is crowded because of this massive creature, over 9 feet
tall.  Its hide is a thick and rubbery, a mottled green that matches
its writhing hair.
4245.room_name: Chained to the wall is a troll.

4246.name: an ettin~
description:
Huge and two-headed, this creature would be intimidating were it
not chained to the wall.  With thick, muscled arms and legs, it is a
powerhouse, though it stands only 10 feet tall - it is young yet for
its kind.
4246.room_name: A huge ettin crouches here, its head reaching the ceiling.

4247.name: a lamia~
description:
With the torso of a human, this creature has the body of a sleek
lion.  Its long tail twitches and its hair is long and black.
4247.room_name: Lying by the wall is a lamia.

4248.name: a dragonne~
description:
A regal creature, this lion-looking beast has brass colored wings. 
In place of fur, brass scales cover its body.
4248.room_name: There is a dragonne sitting regally in the room.

4249.name: dire bear~
description:
A huge, black bear, this creature has midnight fur.  Its eyes, when
open, have a spark of intelligence most bears do not.
4249.room_name: Curled up here in a dire bear.

4250.name: a hill giant~
description:
This creature it, well, giant.  His skin is ruddy and tan and his
hair is dark brown.
4250.room_name: Sitting on the floor is a hill giant.

4251.name: a dire tiger~
description:
This might be a tiger, but it is far too huge.  Its sleek, striped
body paces, the padding of its feet more of a pounding.
4251.room_name: Stalking around the room is a dire tiger.

4252.name: a frost giant~
description:
Overwhelmingly large, this giant has icy blue eyes and a chilled
look about him.  His hair is gray and his touch cold.
4252.room_name: A frost giant sits in the middle of the room.

4253.name: a cloud giant~
description:
This gargantuan creature is strongly built and has a grumpy
disposition.  White hair and hazy, pale eyes give him an eery
appearance.
4253.room_name: Resting on the floor is a cloud giant.

4254.name: a mermaid~
description:
The torso of a beautiful woman melts into the blue-green fin of a
large fish.  Her hair is long and sea blue, her skin pale.  A necklace
of shells is around her neck and a shell bikini covers her breasts.
4254.room_name: A mermaid lounges on the rocks.

4255.name: a hippogriff~
description:
Large, feathered wings grow from the back of this strange, white
horse.  Its hooves are replaced with talons and a pointed beak forms
its mouth.  The mane and tail are also made of large feathers.
4255.room_name: A magestic hippogriff is perched here.

4256.name: a kobold~
description:
A small creature, this small kobold has orange eyes.  Its scaly
skin is rusty brown, and two tiny horns adorn its head.  Long and
pointed, its tail twitches nervously.
4256.room_name: Cowering in the shadows is a kobold.

4257.name: a violet fungus~
description:
This curious growth resembles a fungus, but is larger that most. 
Deep purple in color, it has a broad top and a base of roots that do
not enter the ground.  Long leaves wave in the air, seemingly of their
own mind.
4257.room_name: A strange, unrooted violet fungus sways eerily.

4258.name: a dryad~
description:
Looking as an elven woman, this dryad is gorgeous.  Her hair is
long and deep red, offsetting the amber of her eyes.  Her features are
delicate and her figure slim.
4258.room_name: A beautiful dryad rests on the ground.

4259.name: a formian worker~
description:
A giant ant, this creature is the lowest rank of its race.  Four
legs and two arms extend from its body, all spiny and brown.  Large
antenae extend from its head.
4259.room_name: A formain worker chatters angrily, pacing the room.

4260.name: an elite museum guard.~
subroutines:
M exall 4260 4~
M exall 4260 3~
M kill 4261 100~
M fight 4261 100~
4260.room_name: An elite museum guard stand here, blocking your way.

4261.name: a pseudodragon~
description:
Reminiscent of a red dragon, this tiny flying creature has more
brown in its red than its larger cousin.  Its foot-long body is
covered with fine scales, and a two foot tail twists behind it.  The
barbs on its tail appear very sharp, but the pseudodragon's behavior
is friendly.
4261.room_name: A tiny pseudodragon flits through the air.

4262.name: a locathah~
description:
Though humanoid, this creature is obviously more fish than
anything.  Its yellow-green scales shimmer faintly, and its webbed
hands are wide.  In all, it is about 5 feet tall.
4262.room_name: A locathah lays on the rock, lounging.

4263.name: a giant eagle~
description:
The eyes of this massive beast of keen and intelligent as they
follow any who enter the room.  Its wingspan is massive, its pointed
beak long, and the claws on its feet are dangerously sharp.
4263.room_name: Perched on a falled branch in a giant eagle.

4264.name: a troglodyte~
description:
This lizard creature looks partly human, standing on two scaled
legs.  Behind it, a long tail trails on the floor.  Its hands are
almost human, those its feet have long, pointed claws.
4264.room_name: There is a troglodyte crouched in the corner.

4265.name: a grey ooze~
description:
It appears as a small puddle of water, though it moves of its own
accord.  This strange creature is actually a grey ooze, lying in wait
of friend or foe.
4265.room_name: A small puddle has formed on the floor.

4266.name: a vargouille~
description:
A hideous creature, it appears to be a distorted human head
suspended on broad wings.  The wings are leathery and much like a
bat's, and the hair is replaced with writhing tentacles.  Green flame
burns in its eyes.
4266.room_name: A strange, winged demon flies through the air.

4267.name: a stirge~
description:
An overgrown mosquito, there is something batlike about a stirge. 
Its body is short and furry, and it has eight legs with pincers at the
end of each.
4267.room_name: A tiny stirge flies around the room.

4268.name: a blue wyrmling~
description:
This small dragon is barely more than a baby.  It has dramatically
frilled ears and a single, small horn developing on its snout.  Deep
indigo scales cover its body, though they are petite and not nearly as
glossy as an adult's would be.
4268.room_name: A blue wyrmling paces around the room.

4269.name: a kuo-toa~
description:
Rather humanoid in appearance, it has a rounded body and fine,
green scales.  Its arms and legs are slender, feet and hands broad,
and its bullet-shaped head has bulging eyes.
4269.room_name: A kuo-toa swims through the water.

4270.name: a cockatrice~
description:
This deformed creature appears to be part lizard, cockerel, and
bat.  Its leathery wings are larger and its long tail lizardlike,
though it has the body of a turkey-sized cockerel.  It has a bright
red wattle and comb to match its red eyes.
4270.room_name: Resting near the tree is a cockatrice.

4271.name: a grick~
description:
A large aberration, this creature's body grows to a length of over
3 feet, with tentacles from its front reaching another 2.  Its body is
fashioned like that of a giant snake, glistening dark green on its
open and a muted gray on its underbelly.
4271.room_name: Slithering around the room is a grick.

4272.name: an otyugh~
description:
Bloated looking, this creature walks on three legs and has rocklike
skin.  A vineline stalk rises from its body, its two eyes upon it.  A
wide gash forms its mouth at the center of its body, and two long
tentacles grow from its legs.
4272.room_name: Hiding in the shadows is an otyugh.

4273.name: an azer~
description:
With the size and shape of a dwarf, this creature has metallic
brass-colored skin and wears a brass kilt.  Its bare torso is
muscular, and in place of hair and beard are tongues of flame
crackling with heat.
4273.room_name: An azer sits near the wall cross-legged.

4274.name: a rust monster~
description:
About 5 feet long and standing the height of a halfling, this
bug-like creature is covered with a thick and lumpy hide.  Rust red,
its tail is covered with armor plates and its long antennae curve
upward.
4274.room_name: A rust monster scrambles around the room.

4275.name: a green wyrmling~
description:
Hardly older than a baby, this green dragon has scales so dark they
are almost black.  A cluster of hornlets at its brow and chin are just
beginning to develop, and its wings are furled tightly at its sides.
4275.room_name: Wandering the room is a green wyrmling.

4276.name: a sahaguin~
description:
Humanoid, this creature is covered with green scaly skin.  Its long
fingers are webbed, as are its toes, and it stands about 6 feet tall,
when it stands.  Its mouth is filled with sharp fangs.
4276.room_name: Perched on the rock is a sahaguin.

4277.name: a pegasus~
description:
With two large, feathered wings, this pure white horse is larger
than most.  Its mane is short and its tail long and flowing.  The
hooves on its feet are sharp and jet black.
4277.room_name: A pegasus paces around the room.

4278.name: a shocker lizard~
description:
Dark blue, this relatively small lizard had a bullet-shaped head
and spikey ears.  Its tail is long and pointed, marked with blue-black
stripes.  From time to time, electrical shocks zap along its body.
4278.room_name: Crowded in the middle of the room, a shocker lizard watches.

4279.name: a sea lion~
description:
This is not your day to day sealion.  Its head is that of a
mammalian lion covered in scales, and it has wide, scaled forepaws. 
Its body is long and sleek, its broad fish tail a shimmering green.
4279.room_name: A sea lion lurks under the surface.

4280.name: a thoqqua~
description:
A large, worm-like creature, its body appears to be aflame.  It
glows orange-white with heat and is about 4 feet long.

4281.name: an aranea~
description:
Big freaking spider.  Its body is 3 feet long and its leg span
almost 7 feet.  Two arms extend below its mandibles, each with a hand.
4281.room_name: An aranea sits in its web placidly.

4282.name: a red wyrmling~
description:
With small, scarlet scales, this tiny dragon is barely more than a
baby.  Its barely developed wings are a dull red, as far the small
frills along its neck.
4282.room_name: A red wyrmling sleeps sounded here.

4283.name: a skum~
description:
A strange cross between human and fish, its arms and legs are
deformed fins.  Its back is unnaturally bent, lined with a spiny
frill.  Strength is apparent in its muscled body.
4283.room_name: Swimming around in circles, a skum lurks.

4284.name: a harpy~
description:
With the torso or an old hag, this creature has the lower body and
wings of a birdlike dinosaur.  Its hair is filthy and tangled and its
eyes are coal black.
4284.room_name: Looking sullen, a harpy sits here.

4285.name: a 5-headed hydra~
description:
Its massive body is gray-brown and its belly tan.  The eyes on each
of its five headed are amber.  Its body is shaped like a reptile, a
long tail dragging behind it.
4285.room_name: Roaming the room is a 5-headed hydra.

4286.name: an ochre jelly~
description:
The stones here appear to be wet, but there is a faint rippling to
the dampness.
4286.room_name: There is a wet section of stone on the floor.

4287.name: a magmin~
description:
Small but humanoid, thie creature looks like a tiny old man carved
from molten rock.  Flames adorn its head like hair.
4287.room_name: Squatting near the wall, a magmin lights the shadow.

4288.name: an ettercap~
description:
Standing on two feet, there is little in common between this
creature and a human.  It has two long, dangly arms that reach to the
floor, and its head and body is that of a bloated spider.
4288.room_name: Scrambling around the shadows, an ettercap lurks.

4289.name: a dragon turtle~
description:
Rough and deep green, its shell reflects the light and it much the
same color of sea water.  Its legs, tail, and head are a lighter green
flecked with gold, and golden spines cap its head.
4289.room_name: A dragon turtle swims in a giant tank of water.

4290.name: a griffon~
description:
A majestic cross between lion and eagle, this creature holds itself
with dignity.  It has a muscular lion's body but the head and wings of
an eagle.  Its paws end with long, pointed talons, and its tail is a
mixture of fur and feather.
4290.room_name: Regal of stature, a griffon rests here.

4291.name: a 7-headed hydra~
description:
Its massive body is gray-brown and its belly tan.  They eyes on
each of its seven heads are amber.  Its body is shaped like a reptile,
a long tail dragging behind it.
4291.room_name: A 7-headed hydra prowls in the shadows.

4292.name: a shambling mound~
description:
Were it not moving, this would appear to be a heap of rotting
vegetation.  It has two huge, armlike appendages and is about 8 feet
in girth.

4293.name: a howler~
description:
With long, gangly legs, this creature walks on all fours.  It has
long spikes for hair and a straight, quasi-humanoid face.
4293.room_name: Laying on the floor is a howler.

4294.name: a phase spider~
description: Spider. Big freaking spider. Urg, I hate this floor.
4294.room_name: Creeping around the edges of the room is a phase spider.

4295.name: a white wyrmling~
description:
The smallest of the dragons, this tiny one is just older than a
baby.  Its scales are so white they are almost mirrors, shining in the
light.
4295.room_name: A white wyrmling stares up at you.

4296.name: an elasmosaurus~
description:
One of the mighty lizards, this creature is huge.  It has a thick,
ovoid body and a long tail.  In place of legs, it has broad fins that
can be used for both swimming and walking.
4296.room_name: Crammed into too small a room, an elasmosaurus looks uncomfortable here.

4297.name: a hieracosphinx~
description:
This creature's body is that or a magnificent lion, powerful and
muscular.  Its head, however, is that of a giant falcon.  It has
large, feathered wings that grow from its back.
4297.room_name: Laying regally on the floor is a hieracosphinx.

4298.name: a basilisk~
description:
A short, reptilian creature, it has a dull brown body and it low to
the ground.  A single row of bony spines runs along its back, and
there is a short, curved horn on its nose.  Its eyes glow an erry,
pale green.
4298.room_name: A basilisk meanders around the room lazily.

4299.name: a tendriculos~
description:
Looking as a large plant, this creature is about 12 feet high.  It
is supported by various vines and branches, and two large veins act as
'arms.' Its wide, gaping mouth is filled with sharp thorny teeth.
4299.room_name: Resting on the ground, a tendriculos sits complacently.

4301.name: a janni~
description:
He appears as a man, strongly built and wearing nothing but pants. 
His hair is pure white and there is unnatural strength in his eyes. 
Whisps of cloud surround him.
4301.room_name: Resting here, a janni looks quite noble despite his imprisonment.

4302.name: a spider eater~
description:
This creature resembles a two legged wasp.  It has huge batlike
wings and small forelimbs.
4302.room_name: A spider eater buzzes around the room.

4303.name: a black wyrmling~
description:
With thin and glossy scales, this petite dragon is jet black.  Its
paper thin wings cannot yet support its weight.  Its eyes are sunken
in deep sockets.
4303.room_name: A black wyrmling is trying to fly here.

4304.name: a water naga~
description:
A long, serpentine creature, it has beautiful emerald-green
patterns all along its body.  Its face is mostly human, though its
tongue is long and forked.  Fiery red and orange spines just from its
backbone.
4304.room_name: A water naga glides silently under the surface.

4305.name: a criosphinx~
description:
Its lion-like body is sleek and graceful.  With long horns, its
head is that of a ram, though its eyes have extraordinary intelligence
in them.
4305.room_name: Curled up against the wall, a criosphinx rests.

4306.name: a spirit naga~
description:
With the body of a snake, this creature has crimson bands all along
its black body.  Its head, mostly human, has a scaly look to its skin
and a forked tongue.
4306.room_name: Slithering around the room, a spirit naga lurks.

4307.name: a flesh golem~
description:
Tall and gangly, this creation is made of stolen human body parts. 
Stiched together, it is sickly green, its flesh partially decayed.
4307.room_name: A flesh golem lurches around the room awkwardly.

4308.name: a ravid~
description:
A long, serpentine body that floats through the air makes this
creature distinguishable.  It has a single claw tha tjuts out in an
arm-like manner.
4308.room_name: Floating through the air is a ravid.

4309.name: a formian taskmaster~
description:
A large warrior, this ant-like creature has a bulbous body.  It has
a pair of antennae atop its head and cold, black eyes.
4309.room_name: A formian taskmaster skitters around the room.

4310.name: a young bronze dragon~
description:
The scales of this young dragon are yellow tinged with green,
though a faint shading of bronze has begun to appear.  It has ridges
along its tail and the back of its neck, and an almost playful look in
its eyes.
4310.room_name: A young dragon, bronze in color, sits in the shadows.

4311.name: an aboleth~
description:
A strange combination of fish and amphibian, this creature is about
20 feet in length.  Four long tentacles sprout from behind its massive
head, used for fighting.  It is blue-green in color, gray splotches
marking it.
4311.room_name: In the darkness of the dark, an aboleth swims.

4312.name: a lammasu~
description:
This beast's body is that of a golden-brown lion.  Wings sprout on
its back, great feathered wings like an eagle's, and its tail is of
the same feathers.  Its face, surrounded by a mane of hair, is that of
a noble human.
4312.room_name: A lammasu sits here, staring at you with a smile.

4313.name: a dark naga~
description:
The deep purple of this naga's skin it well suited to the shadows. 
Its hide is rubbery and covered with fine scales, giving it the look
of an eel more than a snake.  A barbed stinging is on the end of its
tail.
4313.room_name: Coiled in the shadows is a dark naga.

4314.name: a bulette~
description:
Blue-brown plates and scales cover this creature's body.  Its
bullet-shaped head has blue-green eyes with a yellow tinge, and its
mouth is filled with ivory teeth. LANDSHARK!
4314.room_name: A bulette lies on the ground, doing a good impression of a boulder.

4315.name: a tojanida~
description:
Once, this deformed creature may have been a snapping turtle. 
Hexagonal plates make up its blue-green shell, and seven stalks
protrude.  Four are fins, two have crab-like claws, and one hears the
creature's strange, gaping head.
4315.room_name: A tojanida swims around in a large, glass-walled pool.

4316.name: a drider~
description:
Oh, for the love of God, why do so many of these insects have to
look like giant spiders?!
4316.room_name: A drider creeps around the room.

4317.name: a young copper dragon~
description:
The metallic tint to this dragon's ruddy brown scales make them
look almost copper, betraying its heritage.  Its wings are spread,
leathery and underdeveloped.
4317.room_name: A young copper dragon hops about the room playfully.

4318.name: a chuul~
description:
A deformed creature, it appears a mix of crustacean, insect, and
serpent.  It has pincerlike claws, four webbed legs, and a mendibled
mouth.  Tentacles surround its mouth, the same orange-black folow as
its body.
4318.room_name: Waiting below the surface, a chuul lurks.

4319.name: an yrthak~
description:
Reptilian, this creature has fleshy wings and a large fin on its
back.  Its tail is long and narrow, and it has a horn protruding from
its head where its eyes would be.
4319.room_name: An yrthak rests here, wings folded.

4320.name: a destrachan~
description:
With a hunched back and laws claws for hands, this creature is
vaguely reptile-like.  It has a tube shaped head, featureless except
for its large ears and toothless mouth.
4320.room_name: A stooped, reptile creature stands in the shadows - it's a destrachan!

4321.name: an illithid~
description:
Also known as a mind flayer, this creature is humanoid in the most
vague way.  It has rubbery mauve skin coasted in a light slime.  Its
head has four tentacles growing from it, and its hands have only three
claw-like fingers and a thumb.
4321.room_name: Standing silently near the wall is an illithid.

4322.name: a lillend~
description:
Though it rests upon a serpent's body, this creature has the torso
of an elf.  Its skin is tan and its hair long and multicolored.  From
its back, great feathered wings grow, multicolored and magestic.
4322.room_name: Coiled and sitting quietly, a lillend watches.

4323.name: a remorhaz~
description:
A huge arctic monster, this creature is snow white but pulses with
a faint reddish glow.  It looks like a huge centipede with its dozens
of logs, and it has wide mouth brimming with jagged teeth.
4323.room_name: A remorhaz raises its massive head and looks at your curiously.

4324.name: a young silver dragon~
description:
Regal even in its youth, this dragon has blue-gray scales with
silver highlights.  A ridge runs along its back from the top of its
head to the end of its tail, and its ears are long and pointed.
4324.room_name: Wandering the room is a young silver dragon.

4325.name: a dire shark~
description:
This beast is a shark to the extreme.  It is larger and has more
intelligence in its eyes.
4325.room_name: A fin cuts through the water as a shark swims around.

4326.name: a roc~
description:
A huge bird, it resembles a large, golden eagle.  60 feet from beak
to tailfeather, it is obviously not a simple eagle, though.

4327.name: a 9-headed hydra~
description:
Its massive body is gray-brown and its belly tan.  The eyes on each
of its nine heads are amber.  Its body is shaped like a reptile, a
long tail dragging behind it.
4327.room_name: A 9-headed hydra considers you with all nine heads.

4328.name: a treant~
description:
With barklike skin, thick and brown, this creature looks remarkable
like a tree.  Its arms are gnarled like brackets and legs fit together
to appear like a trunk.  Branches rise from its head to form a canopy
of leaves.
4328.room_name: A treant stands here, looking a lot like a tree.

4329.name: a mimic~
description:
It appears to be an ordinary chest, made of wood and locked with a
key lock.  There are metal bands wrapping over the top, and little of
it is ornate.  But why is it here?
4329.room_name: There is a treasure chest sitting in the room.

4330.name: a blue slaad~
description:
A huge hulk of a creature, this slaad is massive.  Its skin of blue
and its head is wide, mouth filled with pointed teeth.  Two bone hooks
extend from the back of each hand.
4330.room_name: A blue slaad ambles around the room.

4331.name: a frost worm~
description:
Huge and blue-white, this create is a gigantic worm.  Its massive
mandibles are razor sharp and its body is long and thick.
4331.room_name: A frost worm rests here, head on the ground.

4332.name: a young brass dragon~
description:
This dragon is small but friendly looking, even asleep.  Its
supple, expressive lips are unique to dragonkind.  Its small scales
are a dull, mottled brown, just barely showing the brassy appearance
they will gain.
4332.room_name: Sleeping soundly, a young brass dragon is here.

4333.name: a kraken~
description:
This creature is akin to a giant squid, though it is a behemoth of
one and only has eight tentacles.  Six of these eight are shorter than
the others.

4334.name: a couatl~
description:
This creature is often called one of the most beautiful beings in
the realms.  Its body is that of a serpent, sleek and shimmering, and
it has feathered wings the color of the rainbow.
4334.room_name: Flying around the room is a couatl.

4335.name: an 11-headed hydra~
description:
Its massive body is gray-brown and its belly tan.  The eyes on each
of its eleven heads are amber.  Its body is shaped like a reptile, a
long tail dragging behind it.

4336.name: a roper~
description:
This creature looks much like a naturally formed stalagmite,
growing about 9 feet tall.  Crystalline teeth rim around its gaping
mouth, and it has a single eye.
4336.room_name: A roper stands perfectly still, waiting.

4337.name: a rakshasa~
description:
Standing as a man, this creature has the stance of a human but look
of a tiger.  A white mane is in place of hair, and its face is filled
with feline intelligence.

4338.name: a purple worm~
description:
About 5 feet in diameter and 80 feet long, no one would mistake
this for an ordinary worm.  Its body is dark purple and it has a
toothy maw.  On its back end is a poisonous stinger.
4338.room_name: A purple worm is stretched across the floor.

4339.name: a young gold dragon~
description:
Golden flecks are scattered on the dark yellow scales of this small
dragon.  Its body and limbs are sinuous, and it moves with grace. 
Tiny whiskers are starting to grow on its face.
4339.room_name: Standing here with pride is a young gold dragon.
